{\"sentence\": \"And now, with the Olympic Games themselves looming - the flame will be lit at the Stade de France on July 26th during the Opening Ceremony - the flame is set to arrive in Ile de France for the final days of its pre-Games tour.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2559039936889475e-28, \"text\": \"Ile de France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"the flame\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"July 26th\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening Ceremony\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"the flame\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"the final days\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"its pre-Games tour\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:July 14th: What to expect from France's F\\u00eate nationale this year You can see the path below; Sunday The torch relay will follow the July 14th military parade along the Champs-Elys\\u00e9es, at around 12.50pm kicking off a two-day tour of the capital.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6290867074165843e-14, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Jean-Baptiste_Day\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4519267628895386e-26, \"text\": \"F\\u00eate nationale\", \"types\": [\"Q1445650\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Jean-Baptiste_Day\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint-Jean-Baptiste_Day\"}, {\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9992163039517089, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Champs-Elys\\u00e9es\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the path\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"The torch relay\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"the July 14th\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"military parade\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-day tour\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the Avenue des Champs-Elys\\u00e9es to the H\\u00f4tel de Ville, the torchbearers will arrive at the National Assembly at around 1.25pm - ahead of a busy week of politics in the building.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capitole_de_Toulouse\", \"score\": 0.9999999998940439, \"rank\": 1.0613851878236365e-10, \"text\": \"H\\u00f4tel de Ville\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capitole_de_Toulouse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capitole_de_Toulouse\"}, {\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\", \"score\": 0.9999999779483917, \"rank\": 1.9886455651320568e-08, \"text\": \"National Assembly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Assembly\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Avenue des Champs-Elys\\u00e9es\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"the torchbearers\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"around 1.25pm - ahead\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"a busy week\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"politics\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"the building\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Senate buildings and the Pantheon will be taken in as the route crosses the capital's sixth arrondissement between 1.40pm and 2.30pm.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Senate\", \"score\": 0.9335195608137749, \"rank\": 0.03210526602735542, \"text\": \"Senate\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Senate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Senate\"}, {\"begin\": 1509, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pantheon_Books\", \"score\": 0.9999961316259275, \"rank\": 3.868388499292531e-06, \"text\": \"Pantheon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pantheon_Books\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pantheon_Books\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital's sixth arrondissement\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"1.40pm\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 3pm, the relay should arrive at Place de la Sorbonne, pass through the \\u00cele de la Cit\\u00e9 (3.50pm), before arriving at the Place de la Bastille, at 5.10pm.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sorbonne\", \"score\": 0.9999996703168652, \"rank\": 3.2968306386482415e-07, \"text\": \"Sorbonne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sorbonne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sorbonne\"}, {\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00cele_de_la_Cit\\u00e9\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"\\u00cele de la Cit\\u00e9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00cele_de_la_Cit\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00cele_de_la_Cit\\u00e9\"}, {\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Bastille\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Place de la Bastille\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Bastille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Bastille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"(3.50pm\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"5.10pm\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Between 5.50pm and 7pm, relay followers can follow the route from Quai de Jemmapes, where Paris Plages takes place, to the Place du Colonel Fabien in the 10th arrondissement.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1853, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jemappes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.831366810658661e-17, \"text\": \"Jemmapes\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jemappes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jemappes\"}, {\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.741225877927292e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"7pm\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"relay followers\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"the Place\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"du\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"Colonel Fabien\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10th arrondissement\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the highlights will take place between 7.10pm and 8.20pm with the crossing of the Carrousel du Louvre and the Op\\u00e9ra (9th arrondissement).\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2044, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrousel_du_Louvre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carrousel du Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q11315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrousel_du_Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carrousel_du_Louvre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the highlights\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"8.20pm\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"the crossing\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"the Op\\u00e9ra (9th arrondissement\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, the route will end at 11pm on the forecourt of the H\\u00f4tel de Ville, after the procession along Rue de Rivoli.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capitole_de_Toulouse\", \"score\": 0.9999999998940439, \"rank\": 1.0613851878236365e-10, \"text\": \"H\\u00f4tel de Ville\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capitole_de_Toulouse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capitole_de_Toulouse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"11pm\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"the forecourt\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"the procession\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"Rue de Rivoli\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Monday At 8am, on Monday, the torch will leave from Porte de la Chapelle, in the 18th arrondissement, taking in the Route du Sacr\\u00e9 C\\u0153ur, around 9am.\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\"